21.34	McDonald's_legal_cases	McDonald's legal cases	McDonald's has been involved in a number of lawsuits and other legal cases in the course of the fast food chain's 70-year history. Many of these have involved trademark issues, but McDonald's has also launched a significant number of defamation suits, including "the biggest corporate PR disaster in history".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/BigMacCombo.jpg/200px-BigMacCombo.jpg
